This is inspired mostly by SunnyClockwork’s various Yaldabaoth designs. I started this and gave up on it back in 2023, but decided to pick it up and finally finish it. The dark right hands are meant to look like necrotic, dead flesh, while the “cape” is merely a flap of skin, flayed back from muscle.
